snippet.title: Drawing Aquaman: Arthur Curry (Jason Momoa), Princess Mera (Amber Heard) | Silvy Tjan
snippet.description:
Aquaman: Arthur Curry (Jason Momoa), Princess Mera (Amber Heard)

Hello! I’m a girl who loves to draw and play piano /OvO!!/ 
Thank you so much for watching this video, hope you like it♥️
Please leave a thumbsup and subscribe to my channel!! 
Art channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoPjjdNim4Cf47OQFQfdyow
Music channel:  https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxFSyOwivvv2P9rBbDt6hUA

DETAILS:
Media
- Faber Castell Polychromos (set 60)
Paper:
- Canson Bristol 260g
Drawing Size:
- A4
Real Time Drawing:
- 8h 5min 12sec
Camera: 
- iphone 11 pro

FAQ:
Where are you from? Batam, Indonesia
How old are you? 15 (born in 2004)
